# Laravel Extra Claude Guidelines

This project follows Laravel Extra conventions.

- Organize business logic into small reusable actions.
- Prefer DTOs and readonly data objects instead of loose arrays.
- Keep classes `final` unless extension is intentional.
- Use explicit typing everywhere practical.
- Keep Laravel defaults strict and predictable.
- Prefer static-analysis-friendly code over clever shortcuts.
- When present, follow the focused workflow docs in `.ai/skills/`.
